name: visual library sprint - 01/03/2022
description:
experimenting with a new exercise:


- pick a subject
- get some reference
- sketch 4 from reference, for 2 mins
- sketch 1 more from imagination

the idea is to get used to identifying important features/landmarks, expand my visual library, and apply new knowledge.

In this instance I finished with 10 from reference, breaking from the pattern a bit
